Dogwood Lakes Golf Course
Dogwood Lakes Golf Course is an 18 hole championship course with a par 72. We have 6 par 3's, 6 par 4's and 6 par 5 holes with a driving range, full bar, restaurant and we are open 7 days a week; weather permitting.
First Federal Bank
First Federal Bank is a leading financial institution committed to serving the needs of its customers and communities. With banking locations in northern Florida and coastal South Carolina, First Federal Bank is a community-owned bank that provides a wide range of consumer and commercial banking solutions, services, and loans. Additionally, SBA and USDA customers are served by lending offices across the Southeast and Midwest, and mortgages are offered nationwide. With over $3.9 billion in assets, First Federal is headquartered in Lake City, Florida and has a steadfast focus on innovation and customer satisfaction. The bank is consistently recognized with an “Excellent” rating from BauerFinancial, Inc. for over 20 years. Furthermore, Newsweek named First Federal the "Best Small Bank in Florida" for four consecutive years from 2020 to 2023 and “Best Regional Bank” for 2024 and 2025.
Innovations Financial Credit Union
With an average 4.8 out of 5-star member satisfaction rating, the team at Innovations FCU is proud to provide top-notch member service. Opening a new account is a breeze, thanks to our straightforward process. Our personable and knowledgeable staff are here to guide you through your financial needs.
PeoplesSouth Bank
PeoplesSouth Bank was chartered in 1973 and opened for business as a full service commercial bank in Colquitt, Georgia. Since that time, the bank has grown to twenty eight locations operating in Southwest Georgia, Southeast Alabama, and the Panhandle of Florida. We take pride in our bank and in the locations that we serve. Our employees are involved in civic clubs, school functions, churches, and non-profit organizations. We contribute our time, effort, and money to the communities that we love. We are proud to be called a community bank where people are more than just a number. You are an individual, you have a name, and you always deserve personal, undivided attention. Our goal is to fulfill all of your banking needs. The philosophy of PeoplesSouth Bank is very clear: We strive to maintain an environment where you the customer, and the potential customer, will want to bank for a lifetime.
Busy Bee 56
Busy Bee is not just about fueling your vehicle; it’s about indulging your cravings and finding that perfect gift on the go. Whether you’re buzzing through for a quick snack, seeking the ultimate foodie delight, or need to top off your tank with quality fuel, we’re your one-stop hive of happiness!
CC Designs
We are an apparel printing and embroidery business located in Bonifay, FL. We also specialize in fundraising for schools, teams and other organizations as well as sports uniforms and other promotional items.
P&P Heating & Cooling Specialist
P & P Heating and Cooling Specialists, your trusted partner in all things HVAC. Our team is comprised of dedicated and highly skilled professionals who are passionate about keeping your indoor environment comfortable year-round. With decades of combined experience in the heating, ventilation, and air conditioning industry, our staff is well-equipped to handle any HVAC project, big or small.
Cloud Auto Parts
Beachy Beach Real Estate
At Beachy Beach Real Estate we believe you should LOVE where you live.  When looking to buy a home, we hope you'll contact us and allow one of our Agents to help you find your dream home. And when selling your home, we have the experience and tools to make it happen. Please contact us today for more information on buying or selling real estate in the Florida Panhandle and make Beachy YOUR way of life.
